#: includes/admin/class-admin-settings.php:1757
msgid "Rewrite Relative URLs"
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-admin-settings.php:1757
msgid ""
"Also rewrite relative URLs (starting with /) in src and href attributes. "
"Disable if your theme uses relative URLs for non-asset links."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-admin-settings.php:1759
