"Maximum performance. Adds defer/delay JS, async CSS, separate mobile cache, "
"preloading, lazy load for iframes/videos, and disables unused WordPress "
"assets (emoji, embed, dashicons, oEmbed, block CSS). Pro adds CSS/JS "
"combining and Critical CSS auto-generation. May require testing and "
"exclusion rules for compatibility."
msgstr ""

